author: M
title: RUBiS Divisional Squash Tournament Finals
text:
October 25, 2015 | 0 Comments 
Kristen Johnson claimed the RUBiS Divisional Tournament Title, defeating Robbie Maycock in straight games 11-5, 11-9, 11-5. The B Division Final was claimed by Ben Bramlett defeatinf Bill Dickinson in four games 4-11, 11-6, 11-6, 11-6.
